sellerCard.oneLiner: I Build High Performing WordPress Websites
sellerCard.description: A seasoned developer focused on providing reliable solutions that deliver optimal results under any circumstances, helping you achieve your goals. Whether it's WordPress Development, Web Design, or Search Engine Optimization, I am here to help. I prioritize listening and understanding exactly what you need, aiming to produce results that offer long-term benefits for your business. I am eager to support you in your next digital adventure. Let's discuss and create something great together!

description.content:
Are you seeking a professional WordPress Developer to create a unique and visually appealing website that aligns with your brand identity? Look no further!


I'm Shahbaz Kamil, a Level 2 Seller with over six years of experience, including four years of freelancing for diverse clients from bloggers to financial firms. I bring expertise, efficiency, and quality to every project, consistently exceeding expectations and delivering ahead of schedule.


What I Offer:

  • Custom WordPress websites from scratch
  • Redesign of existing WordPress sites
  • Eye-catching landing pages for conversions
  • Website loading time optimization for better UX and SEO
  • Custom WordPress CMS solutions, including migrations and security enhancements
  • Theme and plugin customization
  • 30 days of free support and instructional videos
  • Custom e-commerce setup with Easy Digital Downloads
  • Development of job boards, listing sites, and social media platforms
  • Custom payment solutions and data import tools


Let's connect to build a High-Performing WordPress Website that can add more value and make your Business shine on the web.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will Website be SEO Friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. Website will be well optimized and SEO Friendly.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do I Customize premium themes?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, from last one year, I've been working in customizing WordPress premium and free themes.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How long does it take to build a website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: All website work will be completed within 4-6 days of the active order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What exact information do you need from me to start the work?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I need your Cpanel/hosting logins to install the files. I need information about the website that you want me to build like a Business website, Health website, Fashion website, Online Store, etc. Then I need graphics and content if you have but it's not necessary to start the order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I get your contact details like Email, Skype etc to communicate easily?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, I am sorry this is against Fiverr's Terms of Service. All the communication must take place via Fiverr messaging system and all the payments must be paid via Fiverr.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I am totally new to this "Online Business thing". How does the whole process work?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Never fear, that's why we are here. You can learn about our time-proven process in our process section. I will try to guide you about each and everything step by step. Just do contact me with your question.
